and taking them

888
00:34:06,599 --> 00:34:07,280
to their grandma.

889
00:34:07,360 --> 00:34:08,559
I'll bring them home later.

890
00:34:09,238 --> 00:34:09,839
The thought

891
00:34:09,919 --> 00:34:11,198
of the kids going over there

892
00:34:11,278 --> 00:34:12,959
makes me restless.

893
00:34:13,199 --> 00:34:13,920
Don't worry.

894
00:34:14,000 --> 00:34:14,999
Dami is clever.

895
00:34:15,079 --> 00:34:15,639
Besides,

896
00:34:15,719 --> 00:34:16,798
she can call us

897
00:34:16,878 --> 00:34:18,398
from her smartwatch anytime.

898
00:34:23,039 --> 00:34:24,039
Wrap it up early.

899
00:34:24,119 --> 00:34:25,119
Don't get tired.

900
00:34:25,278 --> 00:34:26,119
Alright, go ahead.

901
00:34:26,199 --> 00:34:27,199
Bye.

902
00:34:27,679 --> 00:34:28,520
Their coffee

903
00:34:28,600 --> 00:34:29,798
is quite tasty.

904
00:34:46,999 --> 00:34:49,199
Once a dashing young man,

905
00:34:49,479 --> 00:34:52,079
now an old geezer.

906
00:34:53,039 --> 00:34:54,559
What is that nonsense?

907
00:34:55,838 --> 00:34:56,838
What did you say?

908
00:34:57,959 --> 00:34:59,718
Who's talking nonsense?

909
00:35:00,119 --> 00:35:01,758
Look at you wallowing in self-pity.

910
00:35:02,798 --> 00:35:04,398
I'm not wallowing in self-pity.

911
00:35:04,679 --> 00:35:06,318
I'm just lamenting

912
00:35:06,398 --> 00:35:08,079
that time spares no one.

913
00:35:08,639 --> 00:35:10,238
Didn't you get changed?

914
00:35:12,438 --> 00:35:13,919
Don't be so cynical

915
00:35:13,999 --> 00:35:15,479
and sarcastic all the time.

916
00:35:15,559 --> 00:35:16,559
Alright?

917
00:35:17,159 --> 00:35:19,158
Does it make you happy

918
00:35:19,238 --> 00:35:20,638
if I wear an old man's outfit

919
00:35:20,718 --> 00:35:21,838
and look scruffy?

920
00:35:23,039 --> 00:35:24,039
Ever since

921
00:35:24,238 --> 00:35:26,439
Xu Kaixin and her kids came,

922
00:35:26,519 --> 00:35:29,278
you've been helping them a lot.

923
00:35:29,398 --> 00:35:31,358
Families should help each other out.

924
00:35:33,199 --> 00:35:34,199
You?

925
00:35:34,639 --> 00:35:36,158
Have you ever done any chores?

926
00:35:36,238 --> 00:35:37,080
You don't even

927
00:35:37,160 --> 00:35:38,758
pick up a fallen bottle at home.

928
00:35:38,838 --> 00:35:40,318
You break the dishes you wash.

929
00:35:40,398 --> 00:35:41,040
Here we go.

930
00:35:41,120 --> 00:35:42,838
When you tried to fix the pipes,

931
00:35:42,999 --> 00:35:44,358
you flooded our apartment

932
00:35:44,438 --> 00:35:45,758
and the apartment below.

933
00:35:45,838 --> 00:35:47,039
You strained your lower back

934
00:35:47,278 --> 00:35:49,599
and were hospitalized
because you moved something.

935
00:35:50,679 --> 00:35:52,599
Were you helping
or being an embarrassment?

936
00:35:52,679 --> 00:35:53,679
I'm warning you.

937
00:35:53,918 --> 00:35:55,158
Don't disgrace me.

938
00:35:55,238 --> 00:35:56,638
Don't cause them trouble

939
00:35:56,718 --> 00:35:57,999
under the guise of helping.

940
00:35:59,639 --> 00:36:01,559
Come on, that's so last century.

941
00:36:01,639 --> 00:36:03,119
Why would you bring it up?

942
00:36:12,159 --> 00:36:13,638
My daughter is not talking to me,

943
00:36:13,718 --> 00:36:15,238
but she's transferring me money.

944
00:36:16,119 --> 00:36:17,479
It's the first time Youyou

945
00:36:17,479 --> 00:36:19,000
(Youyou transferred 8,000 yuan)
transferred me money.

946
00:36:20,438 --> 00:36:21,918
It's 8,000 yuan in total.

947
00:36:23,039 --> 00:36:24,479
She didn't spend much

948
00:36:24,918 --> 00:36:26,119
and transferred it to us.

949
00:36:33,599 --> 00:36:34,798
What could she buy there

950
00:36:34,959 --> 00:36:35,999
even if

951
00:36:36,238 --> 00:36:37,238
she wanted to?

952
00:36:37,999 --> 00:36:38,999
That's true.

953
00:36:42,119 --> 00:36:43,119
Darling.

954
00:36:44,438 --> 00:36:46,119
Regarding Youyou's job,

955
00:36:46,679 --> 00:36:47,679
I'm thinking...

956
00:36:48,639 --> 00:36:49,279
Considering

957
00:36:49,359 --> 00:36:50,838
what happened to her mentor,

958
00:36:51,159 --> 00:36:52,918
she must be in a bad mood.

959
00:36:53,398 --> 00:36:54,040
So,

960
00:36:54,120 --> 00:36:55,358
let's try not to put

961
00:36:55,559 --> 00:36:57,198
too much pressure on her.

962
00:36:57,278 --> 00:36:58,000
Just let it be.

963
00:36:58,080 --> 00:36:59,278
Give her some freedom.

964
00:37:00,278 --> 00:37:01,718
She tends to overthink things.

965
00:37:01,838 --> 00:37:04,238
What if she goes to extremes?

966
00:37:05,079 --> 00:37:05,719
We can't

967
00:37:05,799 --> 00:37:07,119
let that happen.

968
00:37:08,119 --> 00:37:08,839
For now,

969
00:37:08,919 --> 00:37:10,919
let's just make do with it.

970
00:37:10,999 --> 00:37:11,799
Maybe one day,

971
00:37:11,879 --> 00:37:13,838
after her enthusiasm wears off,

972
00:37:13,918 --> 00:37:15,918
she will want to change jobs.

973
00:37:17,878 --> 00:37:18,878
Alright.

974
00:37:19,599 --> 00:37:20,959
Just let it be.

975
00:37:28,599 --> 00:37:32,159
They took the money
and didn't urge me to go home.

976
00:37:33,679 --> 00:37:35,039
So this is tacit consent.

977
00:37:39,999 --> 00:37:40,999
Yiersan.

978
00:37:41,358 --> 00:37:42,999
We have money for an extra meal today.

979
00:37:43,559 --> 00:37:44,559
Yiersan.

980
00:37:49,479 --> 00:37:50,479
Yiersan.

981
00:37:54,878 --> 00:37:55,878
Yiersan.

982
00:38:00,079 --> 00:38:01,079
Yiersan.

983
00:38:08,920 --> 00:38:20,568
(Hu Pei, Male, Jiang City)

984
00:38:30,959 --> 00:38:31,959
National flag.

985
00:38:38,718 --> 00:38:40,838
Mom, I got another A on my essay today.

986
00:38:41,238 --> 00:38:42,238
Good job.

987
00:38:43,758 --> 00:38:44,600
Mom.

988
00:38:44,680 --> 00:38:46,079
I pooped by myself

989
00:38:46,159 --> 00:38:47,758
at kindergarten.

990
00:38:47,918 --> 00:38:48,999
You're amazing.

991
00:38:49,159 --> 00:38:49,799
Mom, you'll

992
00:38:49,879 --> 00:38:51,119
pick us up, right?

993
00:38:51,199 --> 00:38:52,479
I'll pick you up at 9 PM.

994
00:38:54,559 --> 00:38:56,079
What if Dad loses me

995
00:38:56,159 --> 00:38:57,119
again?

996
00:38:57,199 --> 00:38:58,199
No way.

997
00:38:58,519 --> 00:38:59,638
Your grandma will be there.

998
00:38:59,718 --> 00:39:00,959
Even if she loses herself,

999
00:39:01,039 --> 00:39:02,199
she won't lose you.

1000
00:39:03,559 --> 00:39:04,999
Do you know how to drive?

1001
00:39:05,679 --> 00:39:07,039
Stop talking to me for now.

1002
00:39:07,438 --> 00:39:08,639
I'm too nervous.

1003
00:39:14,599 --> 00:39:15,599
Yiersan.

1004
00:39:17,079 --> 00:39:18,519
I knew you'd be here.

1005
00:39:20,238 --> 00:39:21,238
Yiersan.

1006
00:39:27,079 --> 00:39:28,079
Yiersan.

1007
00:39:29,519 --> 00:39:30,798
You don't want canned food.

1008
00:39:31,559 --> 00:39:32,838
You don't even respond.

1009
00:39:34,999 --> 00:39:35,999
What are you doing?

1010
00:39:36,798 --> 00:39:37,520
It will be dark.

1011
00:39:37,600 --> 00:39:38,798
I won't come looking for you.

1012
00:39:44,398 --> 00:39:45,878
That spot is actually sold?

1013
00:39:49,999 --> 00:39:50,759
Someone put

1014
00:39:50,839 --> 00:39:52,079
Calabash Brothers there?

1015
00:39:53,679 --> 00:39:54,400
Master Hu

1016
00:39:54,480 --> 00:39:56,039
does have some business sense.

1017
00:39:57,479 --> 00:39:58,159
But he will

1018
00:39:58,239 --> 00:39:59,559
brag about it somewhere else.

1019
00:40:00,878 --> 00:40:03,039
No, he'd better not brag about it.

1020
00:40:03,199 --> 00:40:04,238
It will be noisy.

1021
00:40:06,758 --> 00:40:07,718
It used to be

1022
00:40:07,798 --> 00:40:08,838
so loud and annoying

1023
00:40:08,918 --> 00:40:10,398
when he was around.

1024
00:40:10,718 --> 00:40:12,639
How come I'm missing it a bit?

1025
00:40:14,479 --> 00:40:15,479
What's wrong with me?

1026
00:40:17,358 --> 00:40:18,358
Let's go.

1027
00:40:25,374 --> 00:40:30,872
(Hu Pei's grave)

1028
00:41:11,758 --> 00:41:12,758
Xiaojiao.

1029
00:41:36,918 --> 00:41:37,918
Hello.

1030
00:41:38,119 --> 00:41:39,878
I'm downstairs at your parents' place.

1031
00:41:39,959 --> 00:41:41,199
Come and pick up the kids.

1032
00:41:41,798 --> 00:41:42,798
Okay.

1033
00:42:05,086 --> 00:42:07,160
(Account number)

1034
00:42:19,398 --> 00:42:20,479
Do you have any decency?

1035
00:42:20,559 --> 00:42:21,758
Why are you hitting me?

1036
00:42:22,438 --> 00:42:23,718
Didn't we agree to give him

1037
00:42:23,798 --> 00:42:25,238
12 hours to make up his mind?

1038
00:42:25,318 --> 00:42:26,798
Time is not up yet.

1039
00:42:29,199 --> 00:42:30,838
This guy is so miserable.

1040
00:42:31,079 --> 00:42:32,158
His wife cheated on him.

1041
00:42:32,238 --> 00:42:33,398
We're scamming him.

1042
00:42:35,079 --> 00:42:35,838
Even scammers

1043
00:42:35,918 --> 00:42:36,918
have sympathy.

1044
00:42:37,519 --> 00:42:38,519
Well,

1045
00:42:38,959 --> 00:42:40,198
let's ask for less.

1046
00:42:40,278 --> 00:42:41,278
No way.

1047
00:42:42,159 --> 00:42:43,199
Business is business.

1048
00:42:43,438 --> 00:42:45,719
Compared to our work ethics,
sympathy is worthless.

1049
00:42:45,799 --> 00:42:47,278
You are so professional.

1050
00:42:47,398 --> 00:42:48,398
So professional.

1051
00:43:20,090 --> 00:43:26,545
